posts.post_title: N142 Honest Duke Cabinet William Nash
posts.post_content:
Beautiful N142 Honest Duke Cabinet William Nash. Probably one of the most gorgeous 19th century cabinet with the full color and amazing 6" x 9" format size. Some surface flaking on the bottom left and the edges. 

SOLD this awhile back
One of my favorite issues of all time.....
